data.description: Welcome to this charming two-story brick home located in Milton.   With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this spacious home offers 2,760 square feet of comfortable living space. Stunning waterfront view of both sunrise and sunset. Open concept kitchen and living area. This home is equipped with two new AC units, ensuring optimal comfort throughout the seasons. Outside, you'll find a fire pit area complete with Adirondack chairs, providing a cozy spot to gather and enjoy evenings under the stars. In terms of location, this home is conveniently situated just a 22-minute drive from Downtown Pensacola, Pensacola Beach is only 31 minutes away.  Navarre Beach is also within reach, just a 36-minute drive away.
